parameters: What's up? Has been in a daze
Would you like some hot water?
You usually beat me when I say this... Is it really okay?
平时我这样说肯定会直接动手的……真的没事吗？
Ah... it's okay... it's just a daze
The fireworks are about to start. Don't be in a daze
烟花快开始了，别再发呆了哦
By the way, what did you want to say to me just now?
对了，你刚才想跟我说什么来着？
I've been thinking recently…how long can we live like this?
我最近总是在想…这样的生活还能过多久？
(Now, can I still say the same thing)
(现在的我，还会说出一样的话吗……)
A rising flame, roaring explosion, and then bursting into the most brilliant light
火光升腾，爆炸轰鸣，然后绽放出最灿烂的光芒
This very moment, the school field and teaching building illuminated under the curtain of night
夜幕下的学校操场，教学楼，在这一瞬间被全部照亮
The cheering and joyful screams of the surrounding students coming one after another
周围同学们的欢呼声、尖叫声此起彼伏
烟花，如同一位不速之客
Involuntarily breaking all the tranquility and stiffness of the night sky
不由分说地打破了夜空所有的宁静和死板
In its unforgettable and unpredictable stance, it challenges all common sense
以它最出人意料又难以让人忘却的姿态，挑战着所有的常识
Shio, is here 2 blocks from you place?
说起来，汐，这里是不是已经距离你家两个路口了？
I mean, you went too far...
这时候就觉得回家路太短了……
We always wish we have a longer way home...
I clearly have the potential of a prophet
我明明很有预言家的潜质
The day before yesterday, I wanted to make up a prank about the legend of the school garden
前天想搞个学园传说的恶作剧
Write down the rain in the diary and it will really rain
随手在日记本写上下雨结果就真的下雨
So maybe the road will be longer in a few days
所以说不定过几天这路就变长了
Ah... sorry... what did you say just now?
I always think you are strange tonight
Nothing, just a little sentimental thinking about graduation
没什么，就是想到快毕业了有点多愁善感而已
Are you going back after graduation?
毕业之后你就要回去了吧？
I don't want to graduate because I want to experience more different school life
我不想毕业是因为想体验更多不同的学园生活
But it doesn't seem like that
I may just be afraid of parting
我可能只是害怕离别吧
I was so scared that I wished time would stay in these days forever
害怕到希望时间永远停留在这几天
But there will always be a farewell day, right?
但是总会有告别的那天的吧？
Yes, there will always be a farewell day
是啊，总会有告别的那天呢
But I can make that day come later
不过我可以让那天晚点来
I want to go to college with you!
I can learn your language and understand your culture from scratch
我可以从零开始学习你们的语言，了解你们的文化
So there is no need to feel sad about it!
所以根本不需要为此难过嘛！
But why don't you ask me if I can stay here?
不过你为什么不问一下我能不能留在这里呢？
